CustomField.description: The API name of a field set used by the Resource Request object. This field set defines the resource requests from opportunity columns displayed when creating a project from an opportunity.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: API name of a field set used by the Resource Request object. Fields in this set define the columns in Resource Request Mappings from Opportunity on the Create Project from Template page.
